#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: semua_data1_log
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS semua_data1_log;

CREATE TABLE `semua_data1_log` (
  `id` int(13) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `aksi` varchar(244) DEFAULT NULL,
  `nama_user` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `id_user` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `waktu` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `data_lama` text,
  `data_baru` text,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM AUTO_INCREMENT=2940 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;
